{"tid":610262,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(請教naive bayesian algo問題)  分析連環殺人兇手嘅行兇規律","createTime":"2018-03-29T17:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T12:05:04.000Z","uid":137768,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc8f5fed20ede86bfbf2d0d265871078d37df9f","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"假設殺人兇手嘅行兇規律係咁:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6fpq72au\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6fpq72au&h=a45c966c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據wiki上嘅equations:<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x2tqg6k9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx2tqg6k9&h=ee47873e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我試下用下啲式:<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7km4b06x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7km4b06x&h=e8a207ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l54d2nhb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl54d2nhb&h=32e1a9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解上面兩個機率加埋唔係1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同埋就咁睇個圖 P(殺人|落雨^打風)點解唔係1/2 因為一次有一次無。。<br />\n<br />\n我想問下係我理解錯啲式plug in錯左啲數定係咁樣嘅情況係因為assume左落雨同打風係conditional independence 所以會有誤差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d2b4707cca603ca0bc28e975314afca92bb34f","tid":610262,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:52:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47dc237804f39324823b30bcb4e8866fe566aefd","tid":610262,"uid":5894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:04:52.000Z","msg":"要independent呢⋯個分子計錯，用唔到條式"},{"pid":"3ad16506e52d0d4eb12f479733a21b935721417d","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d2b4707cca603ca0bc28e975314afca92bb34f","tid":610262,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T18:52:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:49:24.000Z","msg":"1=有 0=無"},{"pid":"731a54bf4bf79372f802f83a8a48308ef6d5b066","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47dc237804f39324823b30bcb4e8866fe566aefd","tid":610262,"uid":5894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:04:52.000Z","msg":"要independent呢⋯個分子計錯，用唔到條式"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:50:05.000Z","msg":"呃 我都係唔係太明 要independent姐係指咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666182f32a584ceae21cea8aa271b84774d53286","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"731a54bf4bf79372f802f83a8a48308ef6d5b066","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47dc237804f39324823b30bcb4e8866fe566aefd","tid":610262,"uid":5894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:04:52.000Z","msg":"要independent呢⋯個分子計錯，用唔到條式"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:50:05.000Z","msg":"呃 我都係唔係太明 要independent姐係指咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:59:38.000Z","msg":"姐係要P( rain^water | kill) = P(rain|kill) * P (wind|kill)先可以照用條式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b946f88aa283624a04e75e412192f25eacf23c","tid":610262,"uid":14091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T20:03:20.000Z","msg":"直接咁計就可以咁<br />\n<br />\nP(殺人|落雨&amp;打風)<br />\n= P(殺人&amp;落雨&amp;打風) / P(落雨&amp;打風)<br />\n= (1/5) <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">五日入面得一日同時中晒3個events</span> / (2/5) <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">五日入面有兩日同時中2個events</span><br />\n= 1/2<br />\n<br />\nP(無殺人|落雨&amp;打風)<br />\n= P(無殺人&amp;落雨&amp;打風) / P(落雨&amp;打風)<br />\n= (1/5) / (2/5)<br />\n= 1/2<br />\n<br />\n你分母就無錯既 如果你想用Law of total probability 雖然你依加個case咁少\bsample<br />\nP(落雨&amp;打風) = <span style=\"color: orange;\">P(落雨&amp;打風|殺人)*P(殺人) </span>+ <span style=\"color: violet;\">P(落雨&amp;打風|無殺人)*P(無殺人)</span><br />\n= 1/3 * 3/5 + 1/2 * 2/5<br />\n= 2/5<br />\n<br />\nBayesian咁講法<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">P(落雨&amp;打風|殺人)*P(殺人) 其實就係殺人既proportion </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">P(落雨&amp;打風|無殺人)*P(無殺人) 就係無殺人既proportion</span>"},{"pid":"941ee5ddd884c86e5898cf744ab6db134216443b","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84b946f88aa283624a04e75e412192f25eacf23c","tid":610262,"uid":14091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T20:03:20.000Z","msg":"直接咁計就可以咁<br />\n<br />\nP(殺人|落雨&amp;打風)<br />\n= P(殺人&amp;落雨&amp;打風) / P(落雨&amp;打風)<br />\n= (1/5) <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">五日入面得一日同時中晒3個events</span> / (2/5) <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">五日入面有兩日同時中2個events</span><br />\n= 1/2<br />\n<br />\nP(無殺人|落雨&amp;打風)<br />\n= P(無殺人&amp;落雨&amp;打風) / P(落雨&amp;打風)<br />\n= (1/5) / (2/5)<br />\n= 1/2<br />\n<br />\n你分母就無錯既 如果你想用Law of total probability 雖然你依加個case咁少\bsample<br />\nP(落雨&amp;打風) = <span style=\"color: orange;\">P(落雨&amp;打風|殺人)*P(殺人) </span>+ <span style=\"color: violet;\">P(落雨&amp;打風|無殺人)*P(無殺人)</span><br />\n= 1/3 * 3/5 + 1/2 * 2/5<br />\n= 2/5<br />\n<br />\nBayesian咁講法<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">P(落雨&amp;打風|殺人)*P(殺人) 其實就係殺人既proportion </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">P(落雨&amp;打風|無殺人)*P(無殺人) 就係無殺人既proportion</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T20:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n補充少少分子都可以expand:<br />\n<br />\nP(打風^落雨^殺人)=P(打風|落雨^殺人)*P(落雨|殺人)*P(殺人)=1*1/3*3/5=1/5<br />\n<br />\nP(打風^落雨^無殺人)=P(打風|落雨^無殺人)*P(落雨|無殺人)*P(無殺人)=1/2*1*2/5=1/5<br />\n<br />\n應該要P(打風＾落雨|殺人)=P(落雨|殺人)*P(打風|殺人) conditional independence 先可以照用條式:<br />\n<br />\nkill wind rain<br />\n1      <span style=\"color: red;\">1         1</span>      <br />\n1      <span style=\"color: red;\">1         1</span>        <br />\n1      1        1<br />\n0      1        1<br />\n0      0        1<br />\n<br />\nP(kill|rain^wind)=P(rain|kill)*P(wind|kill)*P(kill)/P(rain^wind)=(1*1*3/5)/(3/5)=1 咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似有啲人話real world好難搵到啲independent嘅variables 再加埋可能有measurement error 咁係咪其實好多例子都係assume independence咁照計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ecc104c2b6191ba4d01ffccfa72f321b449c05","tid":610262,"uid":14091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:11:17.000Z","msg":"太長唔quote了<br />\n計算上assume independent可以大大減少運算既複雜程度<br />\n例如你有n件events, 如果會independence既話你計算好多時就無得計完一個event再倍大佢, 同埋你仲要consider nC2個interaction添 (A&amp;B, B&amp;C, A&amp;C...)<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提我上面無assume independence<br />\n只係用左conditional prob同埋law of total prob"},{"pid":"6c1a432f15dbf74379a8d93fc83d97b4878a5dcb","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"上面<br />\nP(kill|rain^wind)=P(rain|kill)*P(wind|kill)*P(kill)/P(rain^wind)=(1*1*3/5)/(<span style=\"color: red;\">4</span>/5)=0.75 先啱 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ec05b0e4c472d52b6e58e74256cb3350e6259b","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33ecc104c2b6191ba4d01ffccfa72f321b449c05","tid":610262,"uid":14091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:11:17.000Z","msg":"太長唔quote了<br />\n計算上assume independent可以大大減少運算既複雜程度<br />\n例如你有n件events, 如果會independence既話你計算好多時就無得計完一個event再倍大佢, 同埋你仲要consider nC2個interaction添 (A&amp;B, B&amp;C, A&amp;C...)<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提我上面無assume independence<br />\n只係用左conditional prob同埋law of total prob"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實上面係人手計可能煩姐 但電腦計其實幾易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我發現其實仲有啲變種:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7c8hnp95\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7c8hnp95&h=e2efd2c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLaplace smoothing我都明 唔想令一啲我地sample不足而occurrence係零嘅event影響我地計出黎嘅數都係零 變左無左意義<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/108797/in-naive-bayes-why-bother-with-laplacian-smoothing-when-we-have-unknown-words-i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstats.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F108797%2Fin-naive-bayes-why-bother-with-laplacian-smoothing-when-we-have-unknown-words-i&d=sICc4kSq5BB2p1WEUmJqfzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=af613182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/108797/in-naive-bayes-why-bother-with-laplacian-smoothing-when-we-have-unknown-words-i</a><br />\n<br />\n但呢個classifer 點解可以變左咁樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪做classifer時個purpose有啲唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lewxzh1p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flewxzh1p&h=2950defc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.inf.u-szeged.hu/~ormandi/ai2/06-naiveBayes-example.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjQ95bMo5PaAhUFm5QKHbgrAwEQFjAqegQIARAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw1x9S5FdcZ2PmruxMQd5fSp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.inf.u-szeged.hu%2F~ormandi%2Fai2%2F06-naiveBayes-example.pdf%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjQ95bMo5PaAhUFm5QKHbgrAwEQFjAqegQIARAB%26usg%3DAOvVaw1x9S5FdcZ2PmruxMQd5fSp&d=sICc4kSq5BB2p1WEUmJqfzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=06b24d05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.inf.u-szeged.hu/~ormandi/ai2/06-naiveBayes-example.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjQ95bMo5PaAhUFm5QKHbgrAwEQFjAqegQIARAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw1x9S5FdcZ2PmruxMQd5fSp</a>"},{"pid":"088fde108cef4a02d075a0564c7b9c22068aae2c","tid":610262,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"8ada1341016a2dc42dc3913b546910898eaa04b8","tid":610262,"uid":14091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"其實個如果考慮dependence就好麻煩 even係電腦<br />\n可能我學藝未精 以我所知 如果考慮dependence既做法都會assume multinormality<br />\n否則電腦上做都係好inefficient<br />\n<br />\n先戴頭盔 無學過classifier 就咁睇完消化 有錯希望有人指正<br />\n<br />\nclassifier個case應該就係general d既<br />\n因為圖1分子既count(w,c)其實就係圖2既n_c<br />\n圖2分子既mp就係圖1既分子既&quot;+1&quot; （如果無理解錯係因為佢training set conservatively assume得1個vocab係有w同c）<br />\n<br />\n所以圖2應該係一個general既classifier algorithm<br />\n仲可以keep著update添<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以現有data計完P(a|v)，之後有新data，用P(a|v)=p，update新既P*(a|v)</span>"},{"pid":"96ec7a2e667fafb04849136417d32d735393d6a0","tid":610262,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ada1341016a2dc42dc3913b546910898eaa04b8","tid":610262,"uid":14091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"其實個如果考慮dependence就好麻煩 even係電腦<br />\n可能我學藝未精 以我所知 如果考慮dependence既做法都會assume multinormality<br />\n否則電腦上做都係好inefficient<br />\n<br />\n先戴頭盔 無學過classifier 就咁睇完消化 有錯希望有人指正<br />\n<br />\nclassifier個case應該就係general d既<br />\n因為圖1分子既count(w,c)其實就係圖2既n_c<br />\n圖2分子既mp就係圖1既分子既&quot;+1&quot; （如果無理解錯係因為佢training set conservatively assume得1個vocab係有w同c）<br />\n<br />\n所以圖2應該係一個general既classifier algorithm<br />\n仲可以keep著update添<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以現有data計完P(a|v)，之後有新data，用P(a|v)=p，update新既P*(a|v)</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"唔係太理解 消化緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係太明咩叫multinormality<br />\n我只係諗要考慮dependence其實等於直接計<br />\nP(kill^wind^rain)就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係數翻有幾多個case係3樣一齊發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能呢個case太簡單定我諗錯方向?<br />\n<br />\n如果有嘅話 Ching可唔可介紹啲source俾我睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}